data.description: NEW PRICE! MOTIVATED SELLER! LANSING SCHOOLS! Two blocks from new Intermediate School! Established Neighborhood and large city lot with chain link fences back yard.  Conveniently located near city convenient store and shopping centers. Three bedroom Side/Side Split setting on large city fenced lot, beautiful trees on lot and oversized deck. Features include: Vaulted living room w/WBFP, Country Kitchen w/center Island cook top with large exhaust fan, Stainless steel appliances in kitchen, refrigerator does not stay. Laminated floors throughout, Master Bedroom w/vaulted ceiling and his/her closets including walk-in closet, and recreation room in basement. Large 8x14 storage shed. Laundry in kitchen.
